g.text: I live and breathe creative problem solving and put that to work writing code, designing exhibits, creating art installations and bespoke objects. With over fifteen years of experr-ence you’ll find I’m extremely passionate; have extensive design, fabrication and develo-ment knowledge and bring a unique set of skills and perspective to any team dynamic.

Crystal Growth Projects Time-lapse Photography and interactives of natural crystal growth for many museums,commercial ad campaigns and film projects.• The NAT, San Diego • GOODCOMPANY, New York • LA MER - GENAISSANCE

Design and EngineeringWood, Metal, Electronic, Glass, Composites,Software or Web Development,Microcontrollers & Sensors of all kind, I can take almost any project from the drawing board to finished product.
Strategy and InnovationHundreds of crazy, creative anddemanding projects produced, coupled with a drive to create and iterate provide unique vantage points.
Dynamic Fungi A year long research project toturn our woodshop waste into profit through the cultivation of edible and medicinal fungi.
Air-to-Water BackPackThis Solar and kinetic poweredprototype puts water generation and filtration on your back.This project was part of a larger two-year NSF funded project.
Software and ElectronicsFrom coding to creating custom hardware,I have more than fifteen years of electronicexperience and I’m constantly learning and using the most up-to-date packages.
